author: Andrew O'Reilly
title: Protests against coronavirus lockdown orders spread in North Carolina, Missouri: ‘My rights are essential’
description: Angry demonstrators took to the streets in North Carolina and Missouri on Tuesday to voice their discontent at their states’ stay-at-home orders amid the coronavirus pandemic.
